ed ira investing and a primary reason why many wouldbe investors have shied away from these opportunities in the past our goal at provident trust group is to make selfdirected ira investing more accessible to the average investor “you get the best of both worlds in a selfdirected ira with provident trust group complete control without the headaches of trying to understand and follow the complex transaction rules of the irs all on your own” why open a self directed ira with provident client focused provident is owned and operated by a team of tax attorneys and highly qualified professionals we do not sell proprietary products and are not affiliated with any bank or financial institution what we have to offer is personalized timely service that assists our clients in reaching their financial goals complex transactions simplified the provident approach focuses on delivering clear and concise information to our clients so that they can make wellinformed decisions regarding their investments we handle all the administrative details to assure them that every reporting detail is covered and completed on time all it takes is a phone call to begin your relationship with the professionals at provident though we’d be happy to meet you in person at our las vegas office as well give us a call at  we’d be happy to answer your questions related to retirement savings and investments through a selfdirected sep ira or any other retirement plan options that you are considering get educated   need help we are here for you learn forms  downloads faq call mon  fri am  pm pst     open an account online now   client login advisor login how do i  make a payment initiate a transfer update contact info log in online faqs send us a message provident trust group llc  w sunset rd suite  las vegas nv hours of operation monfri am – pm pst need to give us a call general inquiry   –  sales questions   –  local   –  fax   –  need to contact a specific department customer service assistance infotrustp